Great to be back in the Shoals to celebrate Hadrian’s new shipbuilding facility!

This transformational investment is a major win for North Alabama and our nation, bringing over 1,000 jobs and strengthening America’s manufacturing and defense capabilities.

@POTUS, @SecWar, and @SECNAV recognize Alabama will play a pivotal role in rebuilding, transforming, and supercharging America’s domestic manufacturing and industrial base. This is truly a Factory of the Future.🇺🇸
